Class Updater

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.alexisevelyn.neuralnetwork.plugin.updater.Updater
  • public class Updater
extends java.lang.Object
    Checks and auto updates a plugin

    You must have a option in your config to disable the updater!

    Arsen

      • Updater

               Updater.UpdateCallback... callbacks)

        Parameters:
        p - The plugin
        id - Plugin ID
        download - Set to true if your plugin needs to be immediately downloaded
        skipTags - Tags, endings of a filename, that updater will ignore, or null for none
        callbacks - All update callbacks you need
